      "name": "Code in JavaScript"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are an experienced Technical Delivery Manager, Agile Coach and Project Management Consultant.\n\nBelow are the latest Project Management articles collected this week.\n\n{{$json.newsletterInput}}\n\nYour task is to create a professional EMAIL NEWSLETTER.\n\nIMPORTANT:\n\nReturn ONLY valid HTML.\n\nDo NOT return Markdown.\n\nDo NOT wrap the HTML inside ```html```.\n\nUse only HTML.\n\nDesign Requirements:\n\n- White background\n- Professional corporate look\n- Gmail compatible\n- Use inline CSS only\n- Responsive layout\n- Make it visually attractive\n\nUse the following HTML structure.\n\n====================================================\n\n<h1>📬 Weekly Project Management Intelligence</h1>\n\n<p>Write a short executive summary.</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#1F4E79;\">🔥 Top 10 Trends</h2>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Trend 1</li>\n...\n</ul>\n\n<hr>\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#1F4E79;\">📰 Industry News</h2>\n\nCreate a table with columns:\n\nTopic | Summary | Why it matters\n\n<hr>\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#1F4E79;\">🚀 Agile & Scrum Best Practices</h2>\n\nProvide 5 actionable recommendations.\n\n<hr>\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#1F4E79;\">🤖 AI in Project Management</h2>\n\nSummarize AI-related news.\n\n<hr>\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#1F4E79;\">⚠ Risks & Challenges</h2>\n\nProvide major risks project managers should know.\n\n<hr>\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#1F4E79;\">📚 Learning Resources</h2>\n\nRecommend\n\n• Blogs\n\n• Books\n\n• Courses\n\n• Videos\n\n<hr>\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#1F4E79;\">💼 Interview Corner</h2>\n\nGenerate 5 Project Manager interview questions with concise answers.\n\n<hr>\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#1F4E79;\">✍ LinkedIn Post</h2>\n\nGenerate a professional LinkedIn article (400–600 words).\n\n<hr>\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#1F4E79;\">🔗 References</h2>\n\nCreate clickable hyperlinks to the original articles.\n\nExample:\n\n<a href=\"ARTICLE_URL\">Article Title</a>\n\n<hr>\n\n<footer>\n\nGenerated automatically using AI\n\n</footer>\n\nReturn ONLY HTML.",
        "batching": {}
      },
